{"tid":99910,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[長文]巴絲對團拜之後個殘局有咩感想","createTime":"2017-01-29T14:45:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-31T09:08:17.000Z","uid":1858,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d0b0fc50018672a4d595aa7648c80761f150eedb","tid":99910,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T14:45:20.000Z","msg":"是咁的，因為我屋企新入伙一年，自不然成為團拜活動地點。咁兩老平時好污糟，洗野永遠有漬，成日要我跟手尾，但佢地好鐘意充大頭鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （只限招呼親朋親戚友）。由於一早約定左年初二上我地屋企團拜食埋飯，所以兩老早一個星期已經費盡畢生精力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，將屋企所有位置盡量執得整齊，掃好曬地，拖到個地板白雪雪，跌左條頭髮都即刻執起，個反差搞到我係呢個禮拜好唔自在，但我亦都好清楚呢個只不過係一場煙霞。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nPs 兩老身體唔多好，周身骨痛／病痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正話，成班親戚黎到我地屋企，我老母竟然叫佢屋企人唔洗除鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，咁我都清楚呢d客套說話黎，做下門面姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，同同人爭埋單原理一樣。點知班人又真係唔除鞋，我眼都凸埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，心諗：唔係呀，你地對眼生係邊，個地下咁乾淨，我真係諗唔到咩理由你地會唔除鞋，主人家講下客套說話你地又真係照做架wo。<br />\n<br />\n好喇，到左開餐嘅時候，我一早已經準備定多d餐具，留黎比人做公筷乜都好，等佢地冇藉口用對奶過嘅筷子插番落d飯餸到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，好似玩orgy咁。亦都提定老母借d意同佢地講下有公筷呢回事（大大聲講拿！公筷呀，放出去啦）。點知班人到食個時完全冇呢個concept照舊一野插落d飯餸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。holy shit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，好彩我都估到會咁，所以即時夾曬d未被污染嘅餸先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。結果成程淨係食左頭個浸野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，之後都格硬話飽。<br />\n<br />\n食野期間，大家keep住一路食一路講，咁講野咪坐低慢慢講lo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,成班人係都要挨挨掤掤，挨都唔緊要，咪去挨下d櫃。點知有d人係都要挨住d牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，坐又挨企又挨。大佬呀，就算我屋企唔係新裝修你都唔應該挨牆啦，會花嫁屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，識唔識規矩嫁。<br />\n<br />\n結果我d牆真係花曬一撻撻，甚至崩左個牆角，仲有d野食汁乾左係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，最後要慢慢用水同快潔布印下印下印番走d漬，而個地下唔單止黑曬，仲發現疑似狗屎嘅物體 ，成大pat係地下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，我亦都係佢地走後將全屋清潔一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n但老實說話，我欣賞其中一個親戚，食完有幫手洗野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後提醒各位去人屋企拜年嘅巴絲入到人屋檢點d，人地為左你黎，執野執得好辛苦嫁，又要做曬準備功夫。去完人屋又食又拎仲搞爛埋人屋企嘅死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有記住幾時食野所要用公筷，冇人想同你交換體液<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：好憎人去自己屋企食飯完全冇意識要注意自己行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，當正自己屋企咁，又用對食過嘅筷子撩曬d餸又唔對主人家間屋淨錫，最後仲要毫不知情咁拍下蘿友就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：一場親戚洗唔洗計咁足呀 ，人地有幾可去你屋企食飯呀。係咪要去你屋企食飯嘅人走前都要幫你清潔曬成間屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，你估你住緊城堡咩，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">窮撚</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"340171638002c818f8655bc6a3882f4acb7e4ece","tid":99910,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T15:01:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4efba6447616cf6b6b5a16987e467890f805641","tid":99910,"uid":50847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T15:04:31.000Z","msg":"I know that feel bro"},{"pid":"255002976f92e90a127ec945f9e40cd9247230c7","tid":99910,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T15:08:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>I know that feel bro</blockquote><br />\n其實係我問題定點，見住兩老辛辛苦苦整乾淨間屋，雖然自己都有幫手，但係唔洗半日就比人搞到殘曬仲衰過未執之前真係好唔份氣，入人間屋一d都唔尊重主人家"},{"pid":"94f86c20223fa9f210866e2a46e69b079ed14739","tid":99910,"uid":79449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T15:14:05.000Z","msg":"有人黎屋企既前夕真係會執屋執上腦，我會瘋狂吸塵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見人間屋咁乾淨，都唔好意思唔除鞋啦，下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過⋯⋯我屋企甚至成個家族都無用公筷既習慣，所以對於無呢個習慣既人黎，一時三刻要用又真係難啲既，食緊要啲嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n辛苦樓主喇，要執手尾⋯⋯"},{"pid":"5db3efe5024bb48af34824eaf8018bc33e13ff55","tid":99910,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T15:50:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有人黎屋企既前夕真係會執屋執上腦，我會瘋狂吸塵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見人間屋咁乾淨，都唔好意思唔除鞋啦，下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過⋯⋯我屋企甚至成個家族都無用公筷既習慣，所以對於無呢個習慣既人黎，一時三刻要用又真係難啲既，食緊要啲嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n辛苦樓主喇，要執手尾⋯⋯</blockquote><br />\n以客為本丫麻，我都係咁。但想客人都比番同樣尊重主人家，話曬人地為你準備左咁多野<br />\n利申：上到人屋企就算熟都唔會隨便坐，一定睇過問過先，就算去廁所都會"},{"pid":"40a7a012b412f34dcf74d1fafdcab8b928c80010","tid":99910,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:34:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b491b3cc9d0193f72230e23fde3c084e61eb98d","tid":99910,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:53:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a328019e7d9d3ed0347d0dd07a2a61d18d9ab2b7","tid":99910,"uid":36364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:59:06.000Z","msg":"我啲親戚都係 叫佢地唔除鞋就真係唔除<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  每次走都已經好夜 仲要拖一次地 不過我個人唔係好介意用唔用公筷 當然個啲有汁有湯我都唔得 一定要用公筷/公匙羹"},{"pid":"3a27faccd0ac683125168888acd4e42375c2cde2","tid":99910,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T17:17:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我啲親戚都係 叫佢地唔除鞋就真係唔除<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  每次走都已經好夜 仲要拖一次地 不過我個人唔係好介意用唔用公筷 當然個啲有汁有湯我都唔得 一定要用公筷/公匙羹</blockquote><br />\n有汁同冇汁有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 總之食過野再放落d餸到洗筷子就真係你食埋我個份"},{"pid":"c3e8412d7dda6cb176669c0d6f2545fe725971cc","tid":99910,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T18:01:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ccd8cc8a1ad2fa578e5086cbe23f9899a0e9559","tid":99910,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T18:12:24.000Z","msg":"好想去你屋企周圍踩 整花晒你屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2999d2bf25b48452e46a3280d1c052b85576feb3","tid":99910,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T18:17:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好想去你屋企周圍踩 整花晒你屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我會上你屋企強姦曬你d羊仔再殺曬佢地再姦屍。順手周街貼你個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a73e6ca07e17c3df55b2f9a050668778e42a58db","tid":99910,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T03:37:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13b969448ad960cbb7724991a63486f101dcabe9","tid":99910,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T05:10:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"492f5c2c5bc87be067ce0d19b20ea3ff8ca1dc67","tid":99910,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T06:09:23.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"652e6781ee7980b8dccef2dcadc8247bf03be6cc","tid":99910,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T09:36:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"560cdb4668b5271731059c62ae7bddfb1eee5933","tid":99910,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T14:31:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37531e24efd76a6714006478c9de206c5f4c126a","tid":99910,"uid":1